<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">George Goodwin</ENAMEX> , an account manager at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Royal Bank of Canada</ENAMEX> , adapted a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Lotus Development Corp.</ENAMEX> program called <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Agenda</ENAMEX> to sort through international news wires .
