<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Individual Inc.</ENAMEX> , a new company in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Brookline</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Mass.</ENAMEX> , uses filtering technology developed by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Cornell University</ENAMEX> computer scientist <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Gerard Salton</ENAMEX> , to automatically produce customized newsletters it sends electronically to subscribers by <ENAMEX TYPE="TIME">8 a.m.</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">the next day</ENAMEX> .
