The <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">daily</ENAMEX> newsletter , which is n't widely available yet , will have a base cost of $ <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">2,000</ENAMEX> a year and provides full text of relevant articles under license agreements with <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Reuters</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">McGraw Hill</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">United Press International</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</ENAMEX> press release news wires and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Japan</ENAMEX> 's <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Kyodo</ENAMEX> news service .
