Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Digate</ENAMEX> says that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Beyond</ENAMEX> will refine the product `` so the message will be smart enough to know to come back and bother you again <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">next week</ENAMEX> . ''
